
Howto build on UW2
==================

make a directory and retrieve all the files.

	
unwind the original source

	zcat fwtk-v1.3.tar|tar xvf -

apply the diffs for uw2

	cat fwtk-1.3.uw.patch | patch -d . -p

change directory

	cd  fwtk

copy the build script
	cp ../BUILD.UW2 .
	
Start the build

	sh BUILD.UW2


To clean and rebuild

	make clean
	make



